(120, 'Philodendron', '199', '149', 99, 'product-featured-120.jpg', '<p>Philodendron is a large genus of tropical plants beloved for their diverse and decorative foliage.&nbsp;</p><p>Native primarily to the rainforests of Central and South America, Philodendrons come in many forms â€”&nbsp;</p><p>from vining climbers to upright, bushy types. They are some of the easiest houseplants to care for,&nbsp;</p><p>making them a favorite for beginners and plant collectors alike. Their name comes from the Greek words</p><p>&nbsp;\"philo\" (love) and \"dendron\" (tree) â€” literally \"tree lover,\" referencing their tendency to climb trees&nbsp;</p><p>in the wild.</p>', '<<img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" data-filename=\"base64_3.jpg\" style=\"width: 449px;\"><br></p>', 11, 1, 1, 5);
