(122, 'ZZ Plant (Zamioculcas zamiifolia)', '249', '199', 100, 'product-featured-122.jpg', '<p>The ZZ Plant, scientifically known as Zamioculcas zamiifolia, is a tough, stylish houseplant known for its shiny,</p><p>&nbsp;dark green leaves and incredible ability to thrive on neglect. Native to Eastern Africa (especially Kenya and</p><p>&nbsp;Zanzibar), the ZZ Plant is loved for its tolerance of low light, drought, and minimal care requirements.</p><p>&nbsp;It\'s often chosen for offices and homes because of its durability and elegant, upright form.</p>', '<p><img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\"  data-filename=\"base64_5.jpg\" style=\"width: 449px;\"><br></p>', 5, 1, 1, 5);
