(124, 'Palms Trees', '399', '249', 49, 'product-featured-124.jpeg', '<p>The Majesty Palm (Ravenea rivularis) is a graceful tropical palm native to the riverbanks of Madagascar.&nbsp;</p><p>Itâ€™s prized as a houseplant for its feathery, arching fronds and lush, elegant appearance.&nbsp;</p><p>Despite its tropical origins, the Majesty Palm is relatively slow-growing and requires specific conditions</p><p>&nbsp;indoors to truly thrive â€” namely, high humidity and consistent moisture.</p>', '<p><img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" data-filename=\"base64_8.jpg\" style=\"width: 449px;\"><br></p>', 13, 1, 1, 6);
