(129, 'Dracaena Anita', '1500', '999', 100, 'product-featured-129.jpg', '<p>Dracaena Anita, also known as the \"Anita Cane\" or \"Elegant Dracaena\", is a refined, tropical-looking houseplant</p><p>&nbsp;appreciated for its graceful, arching foliage and tree-like structure. A cultivar of Dracaena fragrans,</p><p>&nbsp;it features long, narrow, glossy green leaves that grow in clusters atop thin, cane-like stems.</p><p>Its upright form and tidy foliage make it a perfect choice for indoor decor, especially in corners, offices,&nbsp;</p><p>or bright living spaces. It adds a soft, palm-like aesthetic without needing the care a true palm would require.</p>', '<p><img src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" data-filename=\"Dracaena Anita base64.jpg\" style=\"width: 449px;\"><br></p>', 4, 1, 1, 5);
